"We use evaluate() with getComputedStyle() to fetch CSS properties like background color.

Agar text color chahiye:

color = await locator.evaluate(el => 
    window.getComputedStyle(el).color
);

Ye kaise kaam kar raha hai?
🔹 evaluate()

👉 Browser ke andar JS run karta hai

🔹 getComputedStyle(el)

👉 Element ka final CSS deta hai

🔹 .backgroundColor
👉 Background color fetch karta hai
const colorBtn = page.locator('#btn-find-color');
const color = await colorBtn.evaluate((el) => {
        return window.getComputedStyle(el).backgroundColor;
    });
